data.name: ConnectorShape
desc: This service is for a ConnectorShape, a specialized Shape, which can be connected to other Shapes or GluePoints.

properties.name: EdgeLine1Delta
desc: This property contains the distance of line 1.

properties.name: EdgeLine2Delta
desc: This property contains the distance of line 2.

properties.name: EdgeLine3Delta
desc: This property contains the distance of line 3.

properties.name: EndGluePointIndex
desc: this is the position of the connectors end point in 100th/mm.
For unconnected end points you can get and set the position. For connected end points you can only get the position.

properties.name: EndPosition
desc: this property holds the index of the glue point the end point of this connector is glued on.

properties.name: EndShape
desc: this property either holds the shape that the end point of this connector is connected to, or is empty when the end point of the connector is not connected to a shape.

properties.name: StartGluePointIndex
desc: this property holds the index of the glue point the start point of this connector is glued on.

properties.name: StartPosition
desc: this is the position of the connectors start point in 100th/mm.
For unconnected start points you can get and set the position. For connected start points you can only get the position.

properties.name: StartShape
desc: this property either holds the shape that the start point of this connector is connected to, or is empty when the start point of the connector is not connected to a shape.
